Ax * a + Bx * b = Cx
Ay * a + By * b = Cy

b = (Cx - Ax*a)/Bx
Ay * a + By * (Cx - Ax*a)/Bx = Cy
Ay * a + By/Bx*Cx - By/Bx*Ax*a = Cy
a(Ay - By*Ax/Bx) + By/Bx*Cx = Cy

a = (Cy - By*Cx/Bx)/(Ay - By*Ax/Bx)

cost = 3a + b
cost = 3 * (Cy - By*Cx/Bx)/(Ay - By*Ax/Bx) + (Cx - Ax*a)/Bx
cost = 3 * (Cy - By*Cx/Bx)/(Ay - By*Ax/Bx) + (Cx - Ax*(Cy - By*Cx/Bx)/(Ay - By*Ax/Bx))/Bx
